---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: help
---
Create a request immediately

Usage: request [OPTIONS] --note <NOTE> <USERNAME> <AMOUNT>

Arguments:
  <USERNAME>
          Exact username with an optional leading @

  <AMOUNT>
          Positive USD amount with at most two fractional digits

Options:
      --note <NOTE>
          Non-empty request note

      --visibility <VISIBILITY>
          Visibility of the created request

          [default: private]
          [possible values: private, friends, public]

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')

Direct request creation writes immediately after validation. It does not prompt and has no `--yes` option. Financial exit code 3 means the request outcome must be verified independently. Do not retry; check `requests list` and the official Venmo app.
